item.title: Dave Gorman's Powerpoint Presentation
item.description: Published Actual London Euston 17:03 17:05 Birmingham New Street 18:27 19:45 Oh dear, very late last night, I almost missed Dave Gorman. The show was due to start at 20:00 and I walked through the door with 5 minutes to spare, just enough time to find the seat. The warm-up act was a guy called Jay Foreman, he was very funny with some witty songs and he was right, moon chavs has stuck in my head.
